title: Refrigerator Lower Dishrack Kit
description: Refrigerator Lower Dishrack Kit ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 14 Reviews PartSelect Number PS2378335 Manufacturer Part Number W10311986 The lower rack provides easy loading with flexibility for small and large items, and helps hold the dishes in place during the wash and dry cycle. The rack measures approximately 22-inch x 21-inch. The rack is light gray in color with wheels included, lower fold down, and a flexrow retainer. This is a genuine OEM part.
